        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Agreement for hire of slave.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>This is to witness that I have this day hired from <persName>Stephen F
Austin judge of this Colony</persName> an <persName>African negro man named John</persName>
belonging to the <persName>heirs of Richard Barret</persName> deced for the term of
three months for which I obligate myself to pay to said <persName>heirs </persName>or their
representative twenty five bushels of corn to be delivered on the
<placeName>Brasos River</placeName> <date n="Fall-1824">next fall</date>.</p>

<p><persName>St Felipe de Austin</persName><date when="1824-04-12"> April 12, 1824</date></p>

<p><persName>Sylvanus Castleman</persName>.</p>

        </div1>
    </body>
